ZADD PCRig 90 CPU
ZADD PCRig 70 GPU
ZADD PCRig 60 MOBO
ZADD PCRig 50 PSU
ZADD PCRig 70 SSD
ZADD PCRig 80 RAM

ZCARD PCRig

// Finding the count of a range
// LESS THAN EQUAL | GREATER THAN EQUAL
ZCOUNT PCRig 70 90
// LESS THAN | GREATER THAN
ZCOUNT PCRig (70 (90
// LESS THAN INFINITY | GREATER THAN INFINITY
ZCOUNT PCRig -inf inf

// Removing Minimum Member-score pair
ZPOPMIN PCRig 
ZSCAN PCRig 0 
// Removing Maximum Member-score pair
ZPOPMAX PCRig
ZSCAN PCRig 0 

// Increasing
ZINCRBY PCRig 10 RAM 
// Decreasing
ZINCRBY PCRig -10 RAM 

DEL PCRig

ZADD parts 90 CPU
ZADD parts 70 GPU
ZADD parts 60 MOBO

// Querying Sortedset
// By default start and stop are indexes
ZRANGE parts 0 100 WITHSCORES 
// Querying by scores including start and stop value
ZRANGE parts 0 60 BYSCORE  WITHSCORES 
// Querying by scores not including stop value
ZRANGE parts 0 (60 BYSCORE  WITHSCORES
// Sorting in Descending order first 
ZRANGE parts 0 2 REV WITHSCORES
// Sorting in Descending order first, Then Limit (skip, limit) 
ZRANGE parts 0 100 BYSCORE WITHSCORES LIMIT 0 2
DEL parts
